OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine and
OL,6,Fdry evening will lead to a largely
OL,7,Fclear night. Some patchy low cloud may
OL,8,Fdevelop later, mainly in the east.
OL,9,FGradually cooling to leave a mild
OL,10,Fnight, still feeling warm for some.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FAnother dry and very warm day
OL,13,Fexpected, although perhaps a little
OL,14,Fmore cloud around compared to recent
OL,15,Fdays, particularly in the south. Winds
OL,16,Flighter adding to the very warm feel.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
