OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FLargely dry and settled throughout,
OL,7,Fwith plenty of sunshine. Temperatures
OL,8,Fare expected to stay very warm by day
OL,9,Fand warm by night.
